Believer in the Convergence:
Name: Rhys Ironsoul
Civilization: Tactilians
Age: 40
Profession: Elder and Spiritual Leader
Brief History: Rhys is a revered elder and spiritual leader among the Tactilians, deeply rooted in the traditions and teachings of his civilization. He firmly believes in the natural order and the power of the Convergence to bring harmony and evolution. Rhys becomes a source of conflict for the main characters, challenging their beliefs and pushing them to reevaluate their actions. His unwavering faith in the Convergence serves as a contrasting perspective within the group.

